00:05:19,170 --> 00:05:21,773
fascinating and important contemporary design discipline.

70
00:05:22,353 --> 00:05:28,875
But still video games within cultural institutions such as the V&A is still rare and unexpected and unusual.

71
00:05:29,575 --> 00:05:33,657
But for any institution that is engaging with design or contemporary design,

72
00:05:34,157 --> 00:05:40,219
video games are a hugely significant force within our culture today.

73
00:05:40,579 --> 00:05:45,560
And as such, they are a medium that institutions need to be engaging with and embracing.

74
00:05:46,001 --> 00:05:48,861
